lost boys of sudan is a documentary film by megan &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and jon &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; about two &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; boys from sudan , santino &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and peter &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , who reached the united states after fleeing the civil war in their country . " orphaned as young boys " in the second sudanese civil war they " survived lion attacks and militia gunfire to reach a refugee camp in kenya along with thousands of other children . " the documentary 's title “ lost boys of sudan ” was originally the name given to the group of southern sudanese youth by united nations aid workers who were monitoring their flight from sudan .